description.en:
The component is the focus of attention of the research object. The conceptual and visual content of a visual object, which may be carried by one or more physical objects or digital resources.  The content of the visual object continues to exist after the last carrier of that content has been destroyed. 

Original:  Rob Sanderson (https://github.com/archesproject/arches-for-science/blob/master/afs/pkg/graphs/resource_models/Visual/Work.json) from Linked Art Project.
